high_descs: Move to the wooden TV stand
Pick up the yellow pencil that is sitting on top of the wooden TV stand
Carry the pencil to the green floor lamp sitting to the right of the sofa
anns.task_desc: Turn on a floor lamp while carrying a pencil

high_descs: Go left and stand in front of the television.
Pick the pencil up from the television stand.
Go left and then left again to stand in front of the lamp with the pink stand in the corner.
Turn the lamp on in the corner.
anns.task_desc: Turn a lamp on with a pencil in hand.

high_descs: Turn left, walk to the tv shelf
Grab the pencil on the TV shelf
Turn left, walk to the floor lamp in the corner
anns.task_desc: Grab the pencil on the tv shelf, turn on the floor lamp
